headline: With ROIC at 19-Year Highs, Is CCL Entering a New Profitability Cycle?
summary: Carnival achieves a ROIC above 13%, a 19-year high, as pricing gains, cost discipline and debt reduction enhance margins and signal a stronger profit cycle ahead.

headline: NORWEGIAN CRUISE LINE DEBUTS NEW BRAND PLATFORM, "IT'S DIFFERENT OUT HERE," AND LAUNCHES NATIONAL AD CAMPAIGN
summary: Today, Norwegian Cruise Line® (NCL), the innovator in global cruise travel with a 59-year history of breaking boundaries, unveiled its new brand identity inspired by its iconic 90s tagline, "It's Different Out Here," along with a first look at its new national TV campaign.
